    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade BMW E46 M3 in pristine, collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. Chassis integrity is absolute, with the critical rear subframe reinforced and the double-VANOS system fully serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Retaining its original factory finish and a flawless interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal performance. Mechanically tight and cosmetically unblemished.",
      "price": 48500.0,
