    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, keeping it garaged and babied since day one. There isn't a single scratch or blemish to be found, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Drop me a message, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
